headline: Blackstone Credit & Insurance Leads $7 Billion Investment in Sempra Infrastructure Partners’ Port Arthur LNG Phase 2
summary: NEW YORK, September 23, 2025--Blackstone Credit & Insurance ("BXCI") is leading a $7 billion investment in Sempra Infrastructure Partners’ Port Arthur LNG Phase 2.
